#CHIP VRC6
#CLOCK 1789772

; VRC6 (Konami NES expansion) - Pulse and Sawtooth Test
;
; VRC6 adds 2 pulse channels and 1 sawtooth channel to the NES APU.
; This tests all three channels: pulse1, pulse2, and sawtooth.

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Pulse 1: melody
c4 d4 e4 f4

g4 a4 b4 c5

; Pulse 2: harmony
e4 f4 g4 a4

; Sawtooth: bass line
c3 . g3 . e3 .

; All three together (brief)
c4 & e4 & c3

r2

#END
